    Given the following schema:
      """cql
      CREATE KEYSPACE simplex WITH replication = {'class': 'SimpleStrategy', 'replication_factor': 3};
      USE simplex;
      CREATE TABLE users (user_id BIGINT PRIMARY KEY, first VARCHAR, last VARCHAR, age BIGINT);
